  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Thread Croatian sausages, pineapple, red onion, and cilantro onto skewers.",
    "3. Brush skewers with a mixture of soy sauce, honey, and lime juice.",
    "4. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes, or until sausages are cooked through.",
    "5. Serve skewers with a side of peanut sauce for dipping.",
    "6. In a small bowl, combine coconut milk and chili peppers.",
    "7. Serve coconut milk mixture on the side as a cooling sauce.",
    "8. Garnish with additional cilantro if desired.",
    "9. Serve hot and enjoy!"
